  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bbe \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bcd, \u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd \u0bae\u0ba9\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Archbishop writes petition against police chief, secretary of defense",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "A writ petition has been filed in the Court of Appeal on June 27 against the Police Chief and the Secretary to the Ministry of Public Security by Archbishop Melkum Cardinal Ranjit Andakai.",
        "The petition states, 'What disciplinary action has been taken against other police officers, including Patriot Tennakoon, for failing to prevent the bombings recommended by the Presidential Commission of Inquiry?' If no such disciplinary action has been taken, it is requested that it be expedited.",
        "The Archbishop also requested the Speaker's Office to provide him with the remaining 87 volumes of the report submitted by the Presidential Commission of Inquiry into the recent Sunday attacks.",
        "However, the Archbishop was informed on June 22 by the Speaker's Office that it could not be provided.",
        "'The remaining volumes are kept in the Parliamentary Library for the use of Members of Parliament only and cannot be published for the use of the general public.' And 'Making them public is a violation of parliamentary bounties.' The reasons for this have been put before us by the Office of the Speaker.",
        "Therefore, the Archbishop noted that the inhumane practice of those who are supposed to bring justice to the victims of Sunday's bombings is extremely painful."
      ],
